The paper proposes a method for merging Symbolic Planning with Deep Reinforcement Learning to address the difficulty of long-term planning in dynamic visual environments. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The visual nature of the tasks being addressed also suggests that the paper may belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of interactive question answering suggests that the paper may also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category.
